Instructions for AI:

Create utils/incident_correlation.py:

def correlate_incidents(timeframe_hours: int = 4) -> list[dict]:
    """Find events that co-occur within a time window across domains."""
    # Query all signal sources within the window:
    # - Cost spikes (WAREHOUSE_METERING_HISTORY)
    # - Failed queries (QUERY_HISTORY)
    # - Failed tasks (TASK_HISTORY)
    # - Failed logins (LOGIN_HISTORY)
    # - Schema changes (ACCESS_HISTORY + OBJECT_CHANGE_HISTORY)
